      <title>标准普尔将 Prospect Capital 的私人信贷基金评级降至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/s-p-downgrades-private-credit-fund-prospect-capital-to-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将 Prospect Capital Corp. 的评级下调至 BB+，即进入垃圾级，理由是这家规模 76 亿美元的私人信贷基金出现亏损且信用质量恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/s-p-downgrades-private-credit-fund-prospect-capital-to-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 23:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
